2-03/ty-article/.premium/denouncing-israel-as-the-new-nazi-germany-hundreds-protest-outside-columbia-university/0000018d-7091-dd6e-a98d-f4b3eca80000</guid></item><item><title>众议院共和党将推动向以色列提供超过 170 亿美元紧急援助的独立法案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-03/ty-article/.premium/republicans-to-push-bill-providing-israel-with-17-6-billion-in-emergency-funding/0000018d-7084-dd6e-a98d-f4a6347e0000</link><description>该法案将于下周提出，正值参议院民主党人和共和党人就边境安全妥协问题进行紧张谈判，该妥协将为拜登的国家安全补充法案扫清道路，其中包括向以色列提供超过 140 亿美元的援助</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 20:02:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-03/ty-article/.premium/republicans-to-push-bill-providing-israel-with-17-6-billion-in-emergency-funding/0000018d-7084-dd6e-a98d-f4a6347e0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙人报告哈马斯在以色列军队撤离的加沙北部地区恢复文官治理</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-03/ty-article/gazans-report-resurgence-of-hamas-civilian-governance-north-gaza-vacated-by-idf/0000018d-6fc6-d4f1-a18d-fff640bb0000</link><description>哈马斯在加沙最大城市卷土重来的迹象突显了该组织的韧性，尽管自 10 月 7 日对以色列发动致命袭击并引发战争以来的四个月里，以色列发动了致命的空中和地面行动</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 17:48:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-03/ty-article/gazans-report-resurgence-of-hamas-civilian-governance-north-gaza-vacated-by-idf/0000018d-6fc6-d4f1-a18d-fff640bb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列男子在自己拥有的餐厅被枪杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-man-shot-dead-at-restaurant-he-owned/0000018d-6fd3-d971-a38f-7ff339a00000</link><description>警方表示，他们已对发生在以德鲁兹为主的北部城镇雅卡的涉嫌谋杀案展开调查</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 16:49:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-man-shot-dead-at-restaurant-he-owned/0000018d-6fd3-d971-a38f-7ff339a00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列监狱管理局前局长表示，极右翼部长本格维尔希望在该机构立足</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-03/ty-articl